<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/3.0.3/normalize.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <title>Home Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Guesspionage</h1>
    <% 
    let buttonRef; 
    let loginButton
    let loginButtonText;

    if (loggedInUser) {
        buttonRef = "/baseQs/"
        loginButton = "/logout/"
        loginButtonText = "Logout"
    } else {
        buttonRef = "/register/"
        loginButton = "/register/"
        loginButtonText = "Login"
    }
    %>

    <% if (loggedInUser) {%>
    <h4>Welcome <%= loggedInUser %>!</h4>
    <div>
        <button type = "submit" class = "playGame">Play Game</button> 
    </div>
    <%}%>

    <% if (!loggedInUser) {%>
        <ul>
            <li>In March 2024, four masterminds joined forces to craft a game specifically tailored for the Wellesley College community, by the community. </li>
            <li>Wellesley students inhabit a unique bubble within the college community, where they similar experiences and everyday lives.</li>
            <li>It's exciting to have a game curated with topics that you literally relate with in your daily life on the campus.</li>
            <li><em>FOR WELLESLEY BY WELLESLEY</em></li>
        </ul>
    <%}%>
    
    <div class="login-container"> 
        <form action="<%= loginButton %>" method="GET">
            <button><%= loginButtonText %></button>
        </form>
        <form action="/insert/" method="GET">
            <button>Insert Question</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        $('.playGame').on('click', function() { 
        const url = "/baseQs/";
        window.location.href = url;
        });
    </script>